# City Snapshot API
 
A Flask API that fetches live weather and air quality data
for four cities using the Open-Meteo APIs.
 
Built as part of the QurioSkill Data Pipelines Workshop.
 
## Endpoints
 
| Route                  | Method | Description                        |
|------------------------|--------|------------------------------------|
| /cities                | GET    | List supported cities              |
| /snapshot              | GET    | Full data for all cities           |
| /snapshot/<city>       | GET    | Data for one city                  |
 
## How to Run
 
```
pip install -r requirements.txt
python project2.py
```
 
Then visit http://localhost:5000/cities in your browser.
 
## Data Sources
 
- Weather: Open-Meteo (open-meteo.com)
- Air Quality: Open-Meteo Air Quality API
